{"tid":1381473,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"要成功發動罷工 有一樣嘢一定要做","createTime":"2019-07-29T08:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T10:01:14.000Z","uid":68194,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ed2176ab9722ddd1dd3bad7a279122ea93f8eb67","tid":1381473,"uid":68194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:50:52.000Z","msg":"係冇大台嘅情況下要發動罷工<br />\n有一樣困難: <br />\n就係冇一個聯絡組織去統合各工會組織<br />\n即使有好多人心入面想罷工都好<br />\n佢地見唔到其他人企出黎就會淆底<br />\n所以如果今次罷工要成功<br />\n一定要有一個類似民陣咁嘅組織<br />\n去聯絡各業界工會 一齊出聲明<br />\n如果有多個組織一齊號召罷工<br />\n就可以將市民對罷工嘅恐懼減到最低<br />\n雖然一直以黎我地都以無大台為傲<br />\n但搞罷工唔可以單靠默契<br />\n一定要有工會組織一齊配合<br />\n先可以滾起個雪球<br />\n令全港人罷工 <br />\n今次真係生死存亡一役<br />\n希望各位香港人係大義當前<br />\n能夠團結起黎<br />\n一嘢收中共皮<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命!</span>"},{"pid":"fa10cf63882ea7bf9768d678a052a94a1816b18e","tid":1381473,"uid":39205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:53:45.000Z","msg":"[推上國際] 防暴警推跌外國婦 施施然離開<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381423</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a4f8c36280240bfcde47b09775e4a68f8ba20e82","tid":1381473,"uid":68194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:58:26.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8924fcd745124617bab1f78663be737b3018c06f","tid":1381473,"uid":229019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WMV3tnr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWMV3tnr.png&h=77fc1786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Rgez2q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Rgez2q.png&h=b86a56fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgkSmHq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgkSmHq.jpg&h=d447c2f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KY6Vjt5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://